        <h1 ><i>About</i></h1>
        <p><b>The saying goes "Practice makes perfect" but have you ever practiced your interview?
        Don't worry, Pre-s has you covered. We will provide a simulation of the interview 
        process by offering questions your may potentially encounter. You will then have a chance
        to provide a verbal response as you would in an interview. With guided feedback based on
        what interviews anticipate in these questions, you can improve your future response to 
        the question.</b></p>

        <p><b>Engage to unlock more questions. Gain confidence for your interview. Maximize chance
        for receivingthe job offer<b></p>

