          <li><h2><b>After finish reading the question, think about it</b></h2></li>
          <li><h2><b>Ready? Click start to record your response for the question</b></h2></li>
          <li><h2><b>Finish recording? You will be transfered to the next milestone</b></h2></li>
          <li><h2><b>Click Play back to review your response, and make self-evaluation</b></h2></li>
          <li><h2><b>Don't forget to give yourself rating(We not recommand select 5 stars, because you can keep improving</b></h2></li>
          <li><h2><b>If you registered, go and check your achievement page, otherwise register to unlock it</b></h2></li>
